<h2 style="font-size:1.5em;margin-top:20px;border:4px solid grey;padding:10px">example 18 : InlinePlaceholder</h2>
<dl>
  <dt>unnamed inlineplaceholder without default value</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,Tom
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>Syntax</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,{@@}
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>inlineplaceholder with defautlvalue:</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,scil
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>inlineplaceholder with defautlvalue:</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,Jim
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>Syntax:</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,{@:scil@}
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>named inlineplaceholder</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,Jim
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>Syntax:</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,{@name@}
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>named inlineplaceholder with default value</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,scil
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>named inlineplaceholder with default value</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,Jim
  </dd>
</dl>
<dl>
  <dt>Syntax:</dt>
  <dd>
    hello,{@name:scil@}
  </dd>
</dl>
